Paper: hep-th/9511060

Date: 1995-11-09

Title: Spectral invariants for the Dirac equation on the d-Ball with various

boundary conditionsAuthors: J.S.Dowker,J.S.Apps,K.Kirsten,M.Bordag

Comments: 13p,JyTeX, some cosmetic changes and a few more comments

Journal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 13 (1996) 2911-2920

The mode properties for spectral and mixed boundary conditions for masslessspin-half fields are derived for the $d$--ball. The corresponding functionaldeterminants and heat-kernel coefficients are presented, the latter aspolynomials in $d$.